Borderton.description: A small city built along the path of the Great Stone Road, near the eastern border of the Morheim Kingdom. Borderton houses an arcane messaging system directly to Korthal. Borderton is the closest city by land to the OAR. It sees often travel and trade, and has since made a name for itself.

Coval.description: Tucked down a separate trail from the Great Stone Road, Coval acts as a place of refuge for weary travellers. Their small population specializes in collection of natural resources, and is the second closest village to the river that runs through the forest. They use ancient pathways to access prime fishing and hunting locations. Additionally is their reputation for a lineage of a Medically trained familly with a tragic past..
